reg_info.full_title: R.R.O. 1990, Reg. 642: SEARCH AND ENTRY WARRANTS

content.content: 1. A search warrant under subsection 33 (7) of the Act shall be in Form 1.  R.R.O. 1990, Reg. 642, s. 1.
content.raw_html: 1. A search warrant under subsection 33 (7) of the Act shall be in Form 1.  R.R.O. 1990, Reg. 642, s. 1.

content.content: 2. A warrant to enter under subsection 33 (8) of the Act shall be in Form 2.  R.R.O. 1990, Reg. 642, s. 2.
